WEBVTT

00:00:28.600 --> 00:00:34.936
I tweeted, #ifafricawasabar South Africa
would be drinking all kinds of alcohol

00:00:34.960 --> 00:00:37.320
and begging them
to get along in its stomach.

00:00:38.960 --> 00:00:40.656
And then I waited.

00:00:40.680 --> 00:00:44.136
And then I had that funny feeling
where I wondered if I crossed the line.

00:00:44.160 --> 00:00:47.336
So, I sent out a few other tweets
about my own country

00:00:47.360 --> 00:00:49.920
and a few other African countries
I'm familiar with.

00:00:50.400 --> 00:00:51.656
And then I waited again,

00:00:51.680 --> 00:00:53.056
but this time

00:00:53.080 --> 00:00:56.496
I read through almost every tweet
I had ever tweeted

00:00:56.520 --> 00:00:58.256
to convince myself,

00:00:58.280 --> 00:01:02.376
no, to remind myself that I'm really funny